Reasoning: The paper deals with investigating polynomials in the denominators of rational solutions of a partial linear difference equation, which is a topic in the field of computer science and mathematics known as difference equations. The paper also mentions algorithms for predicting factors in the denominator, which suggests a focus on computational methods. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms). Other likely sub-categories include cs.SC (Symbolic Computation and Algebraic Manipulation), cs.SY (Systems and Control), cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science), and cs.NA (Numerical Analysis).
